Hannah had nothing to be ashamed of.

747
00:51:42.338 --> 00:51:44.214
I made her feel like she did.

748
00:51:45.549 --> 00:51:48.844
Because I don't tell people
things. like I said.

749
00:51:51.513 --> 00:51:54.850
Five tickets for Sudden Descent. please.

750
00:51:54.933 --> 00:51:57.811
Hey. are you still wearing
that lacy. black underwear?

751
00:51:57.895 --> 00:51:59.188
Yeah. come on. show us.

752
00:51:59.271 --> 00:52:03.233
Oh. Miles and miles of skin.

753
00:52:03.317 --> 00:52:07.029
- All right. ladies. Enough.
- What? It makes me feel free.

754
00:52:07.112 --> 00:52:09.448
Yeah. just keep the change.
Thank you. sweetheart.

755
00:52:14.620 --> 00:52:15.788
So. yeah...

756
00:52:21.001 --> 00:52:22.544
Shit. I forgot my wallet. guys.

757
00:52:22.628 --> 00:52:24.630
- I'll meet you out there.
- All right.

758
00:52:31.553 --> 00:52:32.679
Hey.

759
00:52:34.306 --> 00:52:35.349
Sorry about earlier.

760
00:52:35.432 --> 00:52:37.684
I didn't want them to make
fun of you or anything.

761
00:52:37.768 --> 00:52:39.019
They made fun of me anyway.

762
00:52:39.561 --> 00:52:42.147
Right. I'm sorry about that.

763
00:52:43.190 --> 00:52:44.942
Can I make it up to you.

764
00:52:46.819 --> 00:52:48.487
uh. sometime?

765
00:52:50.072 --> 00:52:51.407
Uh. you were right before.

766
00:52:52.533 --> 00:52:55.869
Maybe it's best if we just
keep this thing between us.

767
00:52:56.620 --> 00:53:00.040
You know. if we end it now. then
it stays good. Not complicated.

768
00:53:02.292 --> 00:53:03.292
Yeah.

769
00:53:04.503 --> 00:53:07.089
Yeah. no. that sounds good.

770
00:53:10.426 --> 00:53:11.885
Okay. Cool.

771
00:53:16.515 --> 00:53:18.851
Hannah didn't tell me
how she felt either.

772
00:53:20.060 --> 00:53:23.230
But now... I guess I know.

773
00:53:48.881 --> 00:53:52.050
And I'll be ashamed for
the rest of my life.

774
00:53:53.552 --> 00:53:55.888
And shame burns.

